collectionMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Digitised Sound and Video Recordings
collectionMetadata.description:
This dataset is a list of sound and video recordings digitised from the collections of the National Library, Singapore. 

These materials cover a collection of music composed or published by Singaporeans, music produced or published in Singapore, and music related to Singapore.

For enquiries, please email ref@nlb.gov.sg
